<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Welcome to Landson Agri</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style type="text/css">
    /**
     * Reset styles
     */
    body,
    table,
    td,
    a {
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }

    table,
    td {
      mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
      mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
    }

    img {
      -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
    }

    /**
     * Basic styles
     */
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333333;
    }

    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    /**
     * Email container
     */
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    /**
     * Header
     */
    .email-header {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    /**
     * Content
     */
    .email-content {
      padding: 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /**
     * Footer
     */
    .email-footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    /**
     * Button
     */
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table role="presentation" class="email-container" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
      <td class="email-header">
        <h1>Landson Agri</h1>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="email-content">
        <h2>Welcome, {{name}}!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for joining Landson Agri. We're excited to have you as part of our community.</p>
        <p>Your account has been successfully created and is ready to use.</p>
        {{#if verificationUrl}}
        <p>Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
        </p>
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{verificationUrl}}</p>
        {{/if}}
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Landson Agri Team</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Landson Agri. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a> | 
          <a href="{{termsUrl}}">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html> 